    <article class=3D"markdown-body entry-content container-lg" itemprop=3D=
"text" deep=3D"10"><p dir=3D"auto">Adding extra probes around walls (detroi=
t become human)</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://twvideo01.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2018/presentations/=
CAURANT_GUILLAUME_The_Lighting_Technology.pdf#page=3D64" rel=3D"nofollow">h=
ttps://twvideo01.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2018/presentations/CAURANT_GUILLAUM=
E_The_Lighting_Technology.pdf#page=3D64</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Offset along "bent normal"</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DERlcRbRoJF0&amp;t=3D34m35s=
" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DERlcRbRoJF0&amp;t=3D34=
m35s</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Approximate probe-visibility with cubemap (causes "shadowma=
p"-like artefacts), DDGI, McGuire</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://research.nvidia.com/sites/default/files/pubs/2017-02=
_Real-Time-Global-Illumination/light-field-probes-final.pdf" rel=3D"nofollo=
w">https://research.nvidia.com/sites/default/files/pubs/2017-02_Real-Time-G=
lobal-Illumination/light-field-probes-final.pdf</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://developer.download.nvidia.com/video/gputechconf/gtc/=
2019/presentation/s9900-irradiance-fields-rtx-diffuse-global-illumination-f=
or-local-and-cloud-graphics.pdf" rel=3D"nofollow">https://developer.downloa=
d.nvidia.com/video/gputechconf/gtc/2019/presentation/s9900-irradiance-field=
s-rtx-diffuse-global-illumination-for-local-and-cloud-graphics.pdf</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Build approximate geometry</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://www.activision.com/cdn/research/Volumetric_Global_Il=
lumination_at_Treyarch.pdf#page=3D39" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.activisi=
on.com/cdn/research/Volumetric_Global_Illumination_at_Treyarch.pdf#page=3D3=
9</a>
also</li>
<li><a href=3D"http://mrakobes.com/Nikolay.Stefanov.GDC.2016.pdf#page=3D56"=
 rel=3D"nofollow">http://mrakobes.com/Nikolay.Stefanov.GDC.2016.pdf#page=3D=
56</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://www.gdcvault.com/play/1023273/Global-Illumination-in=
-Tom-Clancy" rel=3D"nofollow">https://www.gdcvault.com/play/1023273/Global-=
Illumination-in-Tom-Clancy</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Save best-probes in voxels - also weigh by angle to normal =
(and other magic)</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"http://advances.realtimerendering.com/s2015/SIGGRAPH_2015_Re=
medy_Notes.pdf#page=3D105" rel=3D"nofollow">http://advances.realtimerenderi=
ng.com/s2015/SIGGRAPH_2015_Remedy_Notes.pdf#page=3D105</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Again, add probes close to walls (but with tetrahedra)</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"http://twvideo01.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2012/slides/Programm=
ing%20Track/Cupisz_Robert_Light_Probe_Interpolation.pdf" rel=3D"nofollow">h=
ttp://twvideo01.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2012/slides/Programming%20Track/Cupi=
sz_Robert_Light_Probe_Interpolation.pdf</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Probe-visibility by "tetrahedral"-shadowmap</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://www.ppsloan.org/publications/CoD_IW.pptx" rel=3D"nof=
ollow">https://www.ppsloan.org/publications/CoD_IW.pptx</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Farcry</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://twvideo01.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2015/presentations/=
McAuley_Stephen_Rendering_the_World.pdf" rel=3D"nofollow">https://twvideo01=
.ubm-us.net/o1/vault/gdc2015/presentations/McAuley_Stephen_Rendering_the_Wo=
rld.pdf</a></li>
</ul>
<p dir=3D"auto">Sebastian Legarde</p>
<ul dir=3D"auto">
<li><a href=3D"https://seblagarde.wordpress.com/2012/09/29/image-based-ligh=
ting-approaches-and-parallax-corrected-cubemap/" rel=3D"nofollow">https://s=
eblagarde.wordpress.com/2012/09/29/image-based-lighting-approaches-and-para=
llax-corrected-cubemap/</a></li>
</ul>
</article>
